titleInfo.title: Supplementary Experimental Data for the Paper entitled Numerical and Experimental Evaluation of Error Estimation for Two-Way Ranging Methods

mods.abstract: This data set was used to present the experimental results in our paper entitled Numerical and Experimental Evaluation of Error Estimation for Two-Way Ranging Methods.
